snippet.title: Amiga Longplay Alien Breed
snippet.description:
http://www.recordedamigagames.org

Played By: ScHlAuChi

Unfortunately a lot went wrong with this video, theres some noticeable audio-desynch sometimes and if you wonder why i suddenly have 1 extralife more, full health and all weapons in Level6, its because the Alien Breed ADFs i used to record this video, crashed after level5, and i didnt want to rerecord the whole game again. As you may also notice in level6 of the other version a few weird audiobugs appear - like playing the intro-th Anyway - maybe someone else is doing another/better recording of this game :) -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
